{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-19",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_19_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 19 - The Russian's Hand",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 2,
  "page_total": 10,
  "page_start_sec": 253.12,
  "page_end_sec": 495.26,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.671,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 253.12,
      "end": 255.8,
      "text": "He looked at the sofa and at Spade again,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 255.9,
      "end": 256.36,
      "text": "sharply."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.7,
      "end": 258.6,
      "text": "You have the envelope?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 259.712,
      "end": 260.58,
      "text": "Spade shook his head,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 260.7,
      "end": 262.88,
      "text": "looking at the sofa and then at the girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.46,
      "end": 265.58,
      "text": "He smiled with his eyes and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.58,
      "end": 267.8,
      "text": "Miss O'Shaughnessy has it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 268.76,
      "end": 269.46,
      "text": "\"'Yes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 269.52,
      "end": 271.28,
      "text": "I have it,' she murmured,"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.36,
      "end": 272.86,
      "text": "putting a hand inside her coat."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.76,
      "end": 274.656,
      "text": "\"'I picked it up.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 275.552,
      "end": 277.14,
      "text": "\"'That's all right,' Spade told her.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 277.504,
      "end": 278.304,
      "text": "\"'Hang on to it.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.78,
      "end": 280.1,
      "text": "He addressed Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 281.58,
      "end": 283.46,
      "text": "\"'We won't have to lose sight of each other.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 283.86,
      "end": 285.78,
      "text": "I can have the falcon brought here.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.912,
      "end": 289.62,
      "text": "\"'An excellent idea,' Gutman purred.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 290.14,
      "end": 290.24,
      "text": "\"'Then,"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.1,
      "end": 291.32,
      "text": "sir,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 291.48,
      "end": 294.18,
      "text": "in exchange for the ten thousand dollars and Wilmer,"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.42,
      "end": 297.76,
      "text": "you will give us the falcon and an hour or two of grace,"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.04,
      "end": 300.0,
      "text": "so we won't be in the city when you"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.0,
      "end": 301.47,
      "text": "turn him over to the authorities.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.94,
      "end": 304.8,
      "text": "\"'You don't have to duck,' Spade said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 305.504,
      "end": 306.18,
      "text": "\"'It'll be airtight.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 307.552,
      "end": 308.14,
      "text": "\"'That may be,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 308.24,
      "end": 308.42,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.58,
      "end": 312.14,
      "text": "but nevertheless we'll feel a lot safer well out"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.14,
      "end": 313.94,
      "text": "of the city when Wilmer is being"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.94,
      "end": 315.872,
      "text": "questioned by your district attorney.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.928,
      "end": 317.728,
      "text": "\"'Suit yourself,'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 318.144,
      "end": 318.66,
      "text": "Spade replied."
    },
    {
      "start": 319.42,
      "end": 321.21,
      "text": "\"'I can hold him here all day if you want.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 322.3,
      "end": 323.38,
      "text": "He began to roll a cigarette.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 324.736,
      "end": 325.84,
      "text": "Let's get the details fixed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 326.912,
      "end": 328.18,
      "text": "Why did he shoot Thursby?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 328.52,
      "end": 330.88,
      "text": "And why and how and where did he"
    },
    {
      "start": 330.88,
      "end": 331.936,
      "text": "shoot Jacobi?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 333.184,
      "end": 334.5,
      "text": "Gutman smiled indulgently,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 334.68,
      "end": 336.16,
      "text": "shaking his head and purring."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.152,
      "end": 337.84,
      "text": "\"'Now come,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 337.92,
      "end": 338.22,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.44,
      "end": 339.92,
      "text": "You can't expect that."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.21,
      "end": 342.28,
      "text": "We've given you the money in Wilmer."
    },
    {
      "start": 342.46,
      "end": 343.52,
      "text": "That is our"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.62,
      "end": 344.65,
      "text": "part of the agreement.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.7,
      "end": 347.74,
      "text": "\"'I do expect it,' Spade said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 348.22,
      "end": 350.0,
      "text": "He held his lighter to his cigarette."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.18,
      "end": 350.18,
      "text": "it."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.5,
      "end": 352.64,
      "text": "A fall guy is what I asked for,"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.78,
      "end": 355.58,
      "text": "and he's not a fall guy unless he's a cinch to take"
    },
    {
      "start": 355.58,
      "end": 356.0,
      "text": "the fall."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.3,
      "end": 357.02,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.06,
      "end": 357.68,
      "text": "to cinch that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.86,
      "end": 359.68,
      "text": "I've got to know what's what.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 360.22,
      "end": 361.48,
      "text": "He pulled his brows together."
    },
    {
      "start": 362.54,
      "end": 363.62,
      "text": "\"'What are you squawking about?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 364.21,
      "end": 366.88,
      "text": "You're not going to be sitting so damn pretty if you"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.94,
      "end": 367.92,
      "text": "leave him with an out.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.344,
      "end": 371.58,
      "text": "Gutman leaned forward and wagged a fat finger",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 371.58,
      "end": 373.84,
      "text": "at the pistols on the table beside Spade's"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.84,
      "end": 374.06,
      "text": "legs."
    },
    {
      "start": 375.52,
      "end": 377.26,
      "text": "\"'There's ample evidence of his guilt,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 377.32,
      "end": 377.52,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 377.78,
      "end": 379.94,
      "text": "Both men were shot with those guns."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.088,
      "end": 381.96,
      "text": "It's a very simple",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 382.1,
      "end": 384.2,
      "text": "matter for the police department experts to"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.2,
      "end": 386.0,
      "text": "determine that the bullets that killed the men"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.0,
      "end": 387.38,
      "text": "were fired from those guns."
    },
    {
      "start": 388.28,
      "end": 388.86,
      "text": "You know that.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 388.96,
      "end": 390.34,
      "text": "You've mentioned it yourself."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.82,
      "end": 391.6,
      "text": "And that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.64,
      "end": 392.4,
      "text": "it seems to me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.68,
      "end": 396.88,
      "text": "is ample proof of his guilt.' \"'Maybe,' Spade agreed."
    },
    {
      "start": 397.44,
      "end": 399.34,
      "text": "\"'But the thing's more complicated than that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.74,
      "end": 401.72,
      "text": "and I've got to know what happened so I can be sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.94,
      "end": 404.02,
      "text": "that the parts that won't fit in are covered up."
    },
    {
      "start": 405.44,
      "end": 407.1,
      "text": "Cairo's eyes were round and hot.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 408.352,
      "end": 411.26,
      "text": "Apparently you've forgotten that you assured us it would be a very",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 411.34,
      "end": 411.92,
      "text": "simple affair,"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.1,
      "end": 412.26,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 412.34,
      "end": 412.62,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.8,
      "end": 413.72,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.32,
      "end": 415.68,
      "text": "He turned his excited,"
    },
    {
      "start": 415.82,
      "end": 416.86,
      "text": "dark face to Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.568,
      "end": 418.18,
      "text": "You see,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 418.26,
      "end": 420.2,
      "text": "I advised you not to do this."
    },
    {
      "start": 420.64,
      "end": 424.12,
      "text": "I don't think it doesn't make a damn bit of difference what either of"
    },
    {
      "start": 424.12,
      "end": 424.5,
      "text": "you think,"
    },
    {
      "start": 425.312,
      "end": 426.4,
      "text": "Spade said bluntly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 427.1,
      "end": 428.18,
      "text": "It's too late for that now,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 428.36,
      "end": 429.46,
      "text": "and you're in too deep."
    },
    {
      "start": 430.26,
      "end": 431.54,
      "text": "Why did he kill Thursby?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 433.024,
      "end": 436.22,
      "text": "Gutman interlaced his fingers over his belly and rocked his chair.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 437.24,
      "end": 437.72,
      "text": "His voice,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 437.88,
      "end": 438.36,
      "text": "like his"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.46,
      "end": 438.76,
      "text": "smile,"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.82,
      "end": 439.82,
      "text": "was frankly rueful."
    },
    {
      "start": 441.472,
      "end": 445.24,
      "text": "\"'You're an uncommonly difficult person to get the best of,' he said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 446.02,
      "end": 447.82,
      "text": "\"'I begin to think that we made a mistake,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 448.04,
      "end": 448.26,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 448.4,
      "end": 450.46,
      "text": "in not letting you alone from the very"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.54,
      "end": 450.94,
      "text": "first."
    },
    {
      "start": 451.68,
      "end": 452.24,
      "text": "By gad,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 452.26,
      "end": 452.96,
      "text": "I do!'"
    },
    {
      "start": 454.08,
      "end": 455.78,
      "text": "Spade moved his cigarette carelessly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 456.76,
      "end": 457.9,
      "text": "\"'You haven't done so bad.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 458.64,
      "end": 460.84,
      "text": "You're staying out of jail and you're getting the Falcon.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 461.92,
      "end": 462.49,
      "text": "What do you mean?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 463.2,
      "end": 466.64,
      "text": "He put his cigarette into a corner of his mouth and said around it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 467.41,
      "end": 468.06,
      "text": "\"'Anyhow,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 468.12,
      "end": 469.48,
      "text": "you know where you stand now."
    },
    {
      "start": 470.18,
      "end": 471.63,
      "text": "Why did he kill Thursby?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 472.896,
      "end": 474.5,
      "text": "Goodman stopped rocking his chair.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 476.064,
      "end": 477.82,
      "text": "\"'Thursby was a notorious gunman,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 477.98,
      "end": 479.62,
      "text": "a Miss Ochanessy's ally."
    },
    {
      "start": 480.256,
      "end": 481.58,
      "text": "We knew that"
    },
    {
      "start": 481.72,
      "end": 485.46,
      "text": "removing him in just that manner would make her stop and think that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 485.74,
      "end": 485.98,
      "text": "perhaps,"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.28,
      "end": 488.82,
      "text": "she would do better to patch up her differences with us,"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.92,
      "end": 489.56,
      "text": "besides"
    },
    {
      "start": 489.92,
      "end": 491.82,
      "text": "leaving her without so violent a protector."
    },
    {
      "start": 492.672,
      "end": 493.22,
      "text": "You see,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 493.28,
      "end": 493.52,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.7,
      "end": 494.46,
      "text": "I am being"
    },
    {
      "start": 494.54,
      "end": 495.26,
      "text": "candid with you."
    }
  ]
}